.SH NAME
irdc4cube \- Daemon for infrared device control
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B irdc4cube
.RI [ options ]
.br
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B irdc4cube
is a daemon that handles input from the Infrared device 
and executes bash commands according to the configuration file content.
.PP
